title: Cruising Around Town (Internal Car Ambiance Recording)
description:
On this episode of Sleep & Relax ASMR, we start up our engines, and take a cruise around town. The recording is exclusively from inside the vehicle, and features general driving ambiance including traffic. Enjoy!
